e.Alt = True / False (KeyDown Alt)
e.Shift = True / False (KeyDown Shift)
e.Control = True / False (KeyDown Control)
e.KeyCode = Asc

KeyCode :
BackSpace	 8
Enter	 13
Shift	 16
Ctrl	 17
Alt	 18
CapsLock	 20
Esc	 27
Space 32
PageUp、PageDown	 33、34
End	 35
Home	 36
(Keys.Left、Keys.Up、Keys.Right、Keys.Down)	 37、38、39、40
Insert	 45
Delete	 46
0 ~ 9	 48 ~ 57
A ~ Z	 65 ~ 90
F1 ~ F12	 112 ~ 123
